WHO   — Nick — the driver at the door
WHAT  — The ambiguous ally: the regime's possible spy who becomes Offred's lover and her uncertain way out in the black van.
WHERE — HMT · THE HANDMAID'S TALE  Framework inputs: The Handmaid's Tale (Margaret Atwood, 1985)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
